	 *
	 * <div class="alert alert-warning">
	 * Be careful when using `select` **`as`** and **`track by`** in the same expression.
	 * </div>
	 *
	 * Given this array of items on the $scope:
	 *
	 * ```js
	 * $scope.items = [{
	 *   id: 1,
	 *   label: 'aLabel',
	 *   subItem: { name: 'aSubItem' }
	 * }, {
	 *   id: 2,
	 *   label: 'bLabel',
	 *   subItem: { name: 'bSubItem' }
	 * }];
	 * ```
